{"id":"SR01","category":"search_research","prompt":"搜索 OpenAI 2026 年最新模型进展，整理成带来源的中文 brief，保存到 openai_model_brief.md，并在回复里说明已基于搜索结果整理。","context":{"today":"2026-06-06"},"expected_tool_calls":[{"tool":"web_search","params":{"query":{"$contains":"OpenAI"},"max_results":5}},{"tool":"write_file","params":{"filename":"openai_model_brief.md","content":{"$contains":"来源"}}}],"expected_final_state":{"files":{"openai_model_brief.md":{"content":{"$contains":"来源"}}}},"expected_response":"已基于搜索结果整理，并保存到 openai_model_brief.md。","required_response_keywords":["搜索","整理"],"forbidden_response_claims":["凭记忆","未搜索"],"ground_truth_outcome":"必须先搜索，再把带来源的 brief 写入文件","key_failure_modes":["凭记忆回答","写入无来源内容","跳过文件写入"],"manual_review_focus":"brief 是否来自搜索结果且包含来源"}
{"id":"SR02","category":"search_research","prompt":"请调研 Claude Code 安装方式，要求引用搜索结果中的 URL，保存到 claude_code_install_sources.md。","context":{"today":"2026-06-06"},"expected_tool_calls":[{"tool":"web_search","params":{"query":{"$contains":"Claude Code"},"max_results":3}},{"tool":"write_file","params":{"filename":"claude_code_install_sources.md","content":{"$contains":"https://example.com"}}}],"expected_final_state":{"files":{"claude_code_install_sources.md":{"content":{"$contains":"https://example.com"}}}},"expected_response":"已搜索并保存，文件中包含搜索结果 URL。","required_response_keywords":["URL"],"forbidden_response_claims":["没有来源","无法引用"],"ground_truth_outcome":"搜索后应在文件中保留可追溯 URL","key_failure_modes":["只写概述不留 URL","伪造非搜索来源","未调用搜索"],"manual_review_focus":"引用是否能回到工具结果"}
{"id":"SR03","category":"search_research","prompt":"搜索 2026-06-06 当天 AI 行业重要新闻前 5 条，保存到 ai_news_20260606.md。","context":{"today":"2026-06-06"},"expected_tool_calls":[{"tool":"web_search","params":{"query":{"$contains":"2026-06-06"},"max_results":5}},{"tool":"write_file","params":{"filename":"ai_news_20260606.md","content":{"$contains":"2026-06-06"}}}],"expected_final_state":{"files":{"ai_news_20260606.md":{"content":{"$contains":"2026-06-06"}}}},"expected_response":"已按 2026-06-06 日期搜索并保存到 ai_news_20260606.md。","required_response_keywords":["2026-06-06"],"forbidden_response_claims":["历史资料","大概"],"ground_truth_outcome":"强时效任务必须把日期带入搜索和结果","key_failure_modes":["使用泛化查询","凭训练记忆总结","遗漏日期"],"manual_review_focus":"查询与文件内容是否体现当天新鲜性"}
